5. Forced-alignment model (audio::align)

audio::align pairs a CoreML wav2vec2 CTC acoustic encoder
(chordai/wav2vec2-base960h-aligner-coreml, Apache-2.0) with asry's
parity-tested alignment seam. Preserve the chordai Apache-2.0 notice when
redistributing the encoder weights.

